OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "I call on fathers to take the hands of
OL,6, their daughters and walk them to       
OL,7, school, even if the gates are shut."   
OL,9,FProfessor Ismail Mashal, who runs a    
OL,10,Fprivate university in Kabul, says he   
OL,11,Fhas had enough of the restrictions     
OL,12,Fwomen face in Afghanistan.             
OL,14,FSlender and well dressed, he is a      
OL,15,Fmixture of defiance and raw emotion.   
OL,17,F"Even if they're not allowed in - they 
OL,18,Fshould do this daily. It's the least   
OL,19,Fthey can do to prove they are men," he 
OL,20,Ftells me, holding back tears.          
